OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780326668
OL,3,CFour people sentenced over 'brutal and
OL,4,Csenseless' Ballymoney murder
OL,6,FThe McCook brothers were also
OL,7,Foriginally charged with murder but
OL,8,Fthose charges were dropped after
OL,9,FAustin, who was a key witness for the
OL,10,Fprosecution, declined to give further
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FMr Justice O'Hara said some would
OL,14,Fcontend the brothers had "literally
OL,15,Fgot away with murder" and it is "not
OL,16,Fmy role to argue with them", but he
OL,17,Fcan only sentence in relation to the
OL,18,Fcrimes they had pled guilty to, adding
OL,19,Fhe felt the prosecution were correct
OL,20,Fto assume murder would not be proven.
OL,26,@vD@ZOUwD@UO]wD@aOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
