OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780326668
OL,3,CFour people sentenced over 'brutal and
OL,4,Csenseless' Ballymoney murder
OL,6,FThe judge outlined a range of lies
OL,7,Ftold by the McCook family to the
OL,8,Fpolice over the course of the
OL,9,Finvestigation, including false alibis
OL,10,Ffrom Easther that were later disproved
OL,11,Fby various means such as CCTV, body-
OL,12,Fworn footage and mobile phone analysis.
OL,14,FThe court also heard victim impact
OL,15,Fstatements from Mr Peck's mother
OL,16,FRosemary and sister Heather.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
