OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780326668
OL,3,CFour people sentenced over 'brutal and
OL,4,Csenseless' Ballymoney murder
OL,6,FRosemary Peck and her husband Derek
OL,7,Fwere unable to have children of their
OL,8,Fown and became foster parents,
OL,9,Ffostering more than 100 children over
OL,10,Fthe years, with some staying for as
OL,11,Flittle as a night and the longest 15
OL,12,Fyears.
OL,14,FThey adopted four children, all
OL,15,Fsiblings and half-siblings, as they
OL,16,Fdid not want to see them split up, one
OL,17,Fof whom was Mr Peck.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780326668
OL,3,CFour people sentenced over 'brutal and
OL,4,Csenseless' Ballymoney murder
OL,6,FMs Peck, who has since been diagnosed
OL,7,Fwith motor neurone disease and
OL,8,Fattended court in a wheelchair, became
OL,9,Femotional and left proceedings in
OL,10,Ftears as her statement was read.
OL,12,FA further statement from Ms Peck was
OL,13,Flater read in which she said the
OL,14,F"justice system has let us down as I
OL,15,Fknow in my heart who is responsible
OL,16,Ffor murdering Steven", adding "no
OL,17,Fmother should have to lose her son in
OL,18,Fsuch circumstances".
OL,26,@vD@AOUxD@UO]xD@_OUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780326668
OL,3,CFour people sentenced over 'brutal and
OL,4,Csenseless' Ballymoney murder
OL,6,FHeather Peck described Mr Peck as her
OL,7,F"protector" and the "most caring,
OL,8,Fkind, lovable brother anyone could
OL,9,Fhave".
OL,11,FJustice O'Hara told the court the
OL,12,Fcontrast "to what the Pecks have
OL,13,Fcontributed to society" as compared to
OL,14,Fthe McCooks and Austin "could hardly
OL,15,Fbe starker".
OL,17,FSpeaking outside Coleraine Court on
OL,18,FFriday, alongside Derek and Heather
OL,19,FPeck, PSNI Detective Chief Inspector
OL,20,FHazel Miller described the murder as
OL,21,F"brutal and senseless".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]oD@UOUqD@EO]tD@JOUuD@WO]vD@
OL,26,AXOUwD@KO]}D@AOU}D@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780326668
OL,3,CFour people sentenced over 'brutal and
OL,4,Csenseless' Ballymoney murder
OL,6,FShe added: "The severity of the attack
OL,7,Fitself, and the callous way in which
OL,8,Fthis victim was left lying on the
OL,9,Fground, shocked an entire community,
OL,10,Fwhile leaving a loving family
OL,11,Fshattered."
OL,13,FMs Miller also read a statement on
OL,14,Fbehalf of Mr Peck's family, saying he
OL,15,Fwas known as their "gentle giant".
OL,17,FThe statement read: "He was incredibly
OL,18,Fcaring and kind, and was deeply loved
OL,19,Fnot only by his immediate family, but
OL,20,Fby all those who knew him and his
OL,21,Fclose friends.
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@KO]wD@TOUwD@aO]yD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,450,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44913
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1780326668
OL,3,CFour people sentenced over 'brutal and
OL,4,Csenseless' Ballymoney murder
OL,6,F"Our lives have never been the same
OL,7,Fsince police called with us at our
OL,8,Fhome in January 2021, and they will
OL,9,Fnever be the same again.
OL,11,F"While we try to get through each day
OL,12,Fas best we can, we take a small
OL,13,Fcomfort in knowing that those
OL,14,Fresponsible have been held
OL,15,Faccountable."
